               BabbleCord!
            </p>
            <div class="flex justify-start my-5% lg:my-3" id="other-chat">
                <div class="bg-gray-200 rounded-lg px-4 py-2 lg:max-w-lg">
                    <p class="text-2xl lg:text-xs text-chat-dark-blue mb-3">BabbleCord</p>
                    <p class="text-4xl lg:text-sm leading-normal">Welcome to BabbleCord</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-end my-5% lg:my-3%" id="you-chat">
                <div class="bg-blue-500 rounded-lg px-4 py-2 lg:max-w-lg">
                    <p class="text-2xl lg:text-xs text-bubble-blue mb-3">BabbleCord</p>
                    <p class="text-4xl lg:text-sm text-white leading-normal">
                        Try sending a message
                    </p>
                  </div>
            </div>
